.TH "drm_vblank_work_init" 9 "drm_vblank_work_init" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_vblank_work_init \- initialize a vblank work item
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" drm_vblank_work_init
.BI "(struct drm_vblank_work *work "  ","
.BI "struct drm_crtc *crtc "  ","
.BI "void (*func)(struct kthread_work *work) "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "work" 12
vblank work item
.IP "crtc" 12
CRTC whose vblank will trigger the work execution
.IP "func" 12
work function to be executed
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initialize a vblank work item for a specific crtc.
